    <item>
      <title>日本央行保持稳定，保持加息时机选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/boj-holds-steady-keeps-rate-hike-timing-options-open</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行在暂时坚持负利率后，不断让投资者猜测其何时会改变政策，同时表示，它对实现长期追求的通胀目标越来越有信心。彭博社的斯蒂芬·恩格尔研究了日本央行政策决定和行长上田一夫新闻发布会后的关键要点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/boj-holds-steady-keeps-rate-hike-timing-options-open</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:18:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国大胆的股市救助计划引来怀疑论者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-s-bold-stock-market-rescue-plan-lures-a-crowd-of-skeptics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国迄今为止最大胆的阻止当前股市暴跌的计划正面临质疑，因为失望的投资者表示，如果不能从根本上解决其陷入困境的经济，任何反弹都将是短暂的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-s-bold-stock-market-rescue-plan-lures-a-crowd-of-skeptics</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛称动量交易者在“每种情况”下都会卖出股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/goldman-says-momentum-traders-to-sell-stocks-in-every-scenario</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，无论市场走势如何，一些交易员都将在下周抛售股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/goldman-says-momentum-traders-to-sell-stocks-in-every-scenario</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:52:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>继东欧债务出售后，罗马尼亚发行美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/romania-offers-dollar-bonds-following-eastern-eu-debt-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该地区其他国家继续发行欧元和美元来为其预算赤字融资后，罗马尼亚将于 2024 年首次利用国际市场，以利用对新兴市场债务的高需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/romania-offers-dollar-bonds-following-eastern-eu-debt-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国刺激计划推动新兴市场资产回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/emerging-market-stocks-surge-amid-china-stimulus-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估了中国经济新刺激措施的可能有效性，新兴市场股市回吐了对中国经济新刺激措施的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/emerging-market-stocks-surge-amid-china-stimulus-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 08:42:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼放弃 100 亿美元印度合并后 Zee 股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/zee-slumps-10-after-sony-scraps-10-billion-india-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zee Entertainment Enterprises Ltd. 取消与索尼集团公司 (Sony Group Corp.) 的 100 亿美元合并计划，引发一系列评级下调，分析师预测这家印度公司的估值将大幅缩水，股价暴跌创纪录水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/zee-slumps-10-after-sony-scraps-10-billion-india-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:56:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度超越香港成为全球第四大股票市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/india-overtakes-hong-kong-as-world-s-fourth-largest-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市市值首次超过香港股市，因为这个南亚国家的增长前景和政策改革使其成为投资者的宠儿，而全球资本正从中国涌出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/india-overtakes-hong-kong-as-world-s-fourth-largest-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国再次打击胡塞武装，布伦特原油稳定在 80 美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国和英国对伊朗支持的也门胡塞武装发起新一轮打击，但由于全球原油供应充足抵消了中东紧张局势，油价仍保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
